{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"???","narration":"\"...me.\"","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"\"Kagome!\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event07","chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.4},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...Huh?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":102001,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"Are you awake?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"That voice...Torte...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"That's right!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"(She speaks so clearly. I thought she was@around the same age as me,)"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"(but she's actually quite young...)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Um...where is this place?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"This is a world called the \"Ark of Feelings\"."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ark of...Feelings...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Yes, it's a place where various people's memories"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"are gathered and turned into books!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Your book is one of them, Kagome."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"This...is my book?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"That's right!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I jumped into it and until just now,"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I was in the world inside your mind, Kagome."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Inside my mind...? Was I dreaming?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I went to the library, and I talked@with Iroha and everyone..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"It didn't feel like a dream though..."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Ah, we went to the library together!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"At that time, Torte...you had become Aru...right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Huh...? What are you talking about?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameNarration":"Kagome","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":150.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:I didn't really understand it,@but Torte is a girl from the 15th century.@She came to the Ark of Feelings@using a certain magic.]","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:...So, this is a place where certain@people's memories are gathered, and each@book here seems to have the memories@of each individual engraved in them.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:When you jump into a book,@you enter that person's mind,@but since it's the \"world inside their mind,\"@it's not reality.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:Torte was just supposed to be by my side,@talking to me normally...@But in reality, she was inside my head,@seeing the future through my eyes.]"},{"progressNarration":"[textBlack:In the real world, it seemed like she@was talking to me through Aru....]"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...Which means...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"In reality, there weren't any books@about Jeanne d'Arc in the library, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I think so! It's something that's actually happening@in the future!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Even that red moon...?@It didn't feel real..."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"That's not true!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"The red moon and the fact that La Pucelle@didn't exist..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Those are things that are really happening@in the 15th century where I am!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Eeeeh...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
